
graycolormap(1)                Scilab Function                graycolormap(1)
NAME
  graycolormap - Linear gray colormap

CALLING SEQUENCE
  cmap=graycolormap(n)

PARAMETERS

  n         : an integer greater or equal than 1, the "colormap" size

  cmap      : matrix with 3 column, [R,G,B] color definition

DESCRIPTION
  Computes a colormap with grays colors varying linearly

SEE ALSO
  colormap, xset, plot3d1, hotcolormap

EXAMPLE
  xset('colormap',graycolormap(32))
  plot3d1()
